###
# WandaTools API Testing
# Install VS Code Extension: "REST Client" to run these requests
# Edit @baseUrl and @token variables below

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = your_access_token_here

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### HEALTH CHECK
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Check API health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Get API info
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTHENTICATION
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Register new user
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!",
  "business_type": "Freelancer",
  "timezone": "Africa/Johannesburg"
}

### Login user
POST @baseUrl/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### Get current user info (requires token)
GET @baseUrl/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Update user profile
PUT @baseUrl/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "phone": "+27764693531",
  "timezone": "Africa/Johannesburg",
  "business_type": "Small Business"
}

### Change password
POST @baseUrl/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_password": "TestPassword123!",
  "new_password": "NewPassword456!"
}

### Refresh access token
POST @baseUrl/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

### Logout user
POST @baseUrl/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### TRANSACTIONS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create income transaction
POST @baseUrl/tools/transactions
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "income",
  "amount": 5000.00,
  "category": "Sales",
  "description": "Client Invoice #001",
  "transaction_date": "2025-06-18T10:30:00",
  "reference_id": "INV-001",
  "recipient_or_payer": "ABC Company",
  "notes": "Payment received for web design services",
  "is_recurring": "monthly",
  "tax_deductible": "Yes"
}

### Create expense transaction
POST @baseUrl/tools/transactions
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200.00,
  "category": "Rent",
  "description": "Monthly office rent",
  "transaction_date": "2025-06-01T09:00:00",
  "reference_id": "RENT-06-2025",
  "recipient_or_payer": "Property Management Ltd",
  "notes": "June rent payment",
  "is_recurring": "monthly",
  "tax_deductible": "No"
}

### List all transactions
GET @baseUrl/tools/transactions?skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer @token

### List transactions with filters
GET @baseUrl/tools/transactions?skip=0&limit=10&transaction_type=income&category=Sales
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get specific transaction
GET @baseUrl/tools/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Update transaction
PUT @baseUrl/tools/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5500.00,
  "description": "Client Invoice #001 - Updated",
  "notes": "Revised amount after approval"
}

### Delete transaction
DELETE @baseUrl/tools/transactions/1
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DASHBOARD
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get current month summary
GET @baseUrl/tools/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get specific month summary (format: YYYY-MM)
GET @baseUrl/tools/dashboard/summary?month=2025-06
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get 6-month history
GET @baseUrl/tools/dashboard/history?months=6
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get 12-month history
GET @baseUrl/tools/dashboard/history?months=12
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DOCUMENTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Generate audit report
POST @baseUrl/tools/documents
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "audit_report",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "period_end": "2025-06-30T23:59:59"
}

### Generate loan application document
POST @baseUrl/tools/documents
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "loan_application",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "period_end": "2025-06-30T23:59:59"
}

### Generate investment report
POST @baseUrl/tools/documents
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "investment_report",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00",
  "period_end": "2025-06-30T23:59:59"
}

### Generate monthly summary
POST @baseUrl/tools/documents
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "monthly_summary",
  "period_start": "2025-06-01T00:00:00",
  "period_end": "2025-06-30T23:59:59"
}

### List all documents
GET @baseUrl/tools/documents
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get specific document
GET @baseUrl/tools/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Delete document
DELETE @baseUrl/tools/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### WANDAAI
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Ask WandaAI - Cash flow insights
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How is my cash flow looking this month?",
  "mode": "insights"
}

### Ask WandaAI - Spending analysis
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Where am I spending the most money?",
  "mode": "insights"
}

### Ask WandaAI - Profit margin
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is my profit margin this month?",
  "mode": "insights"
}

### Ask WandaAI - Cost reduction recommendations
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "How can I reduce my expenses?",
  "mode": "recommendations"
}

### Ask WandaAI - Loan readiness assessment
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Am I ready to apply for a business loan?",
  "mode": "insights"
}

### Ask WandaAI - Business strategy
POST @baseUrl/wandaai/query
Authorization: Bearer @token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What financial goals should I set?",
  "mode": "business"
}

### Get AI modes
GET @baseUrl/wandaai/modes
Authorization: Bearer @token

### Get sample prompts
GET @baseUrl/wandaai/prompts
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SUPPORT & CONTACT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Submit contact form (no auth required)
POST @baseUrl/support/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "email": "john.smith@example.com",
  "phone": "+27764693531",
  "subject": "Technical support needed",
  "message": "I'm having trouble connecting my accounting software to WandaTools. Can someone help me troubleshoot?"
}

### Get FAQ items
GET @baseUrl/support/faq

### Search FAQ
GET @baseUrl/support/faq?search=security

### Filter FAQ by category
GET @baseUrl/support/faq?category=billing

### Get support status
GET @baseUrl/support/status

### Get system health (for authenticated users)
GET @baseUrl/support/health
Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### NOTIFICATIONS (Future)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get notifications
### GET @baseUrl/notifications
### Authorization: Bearer @token

### Mark notification as read
### PUT @baseUrl/notifications/1/read
### Authorization: Bearer @token

### Delete notification
### DELETE @baseUrl/notifications/1
### Authorization: Bearer @token

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### NOTES
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1. Update @token variable with your actual access token from login response
# 2. Update @baseUrl for production: https://wandatools-api.onrender.com/api/v1
# 3. All dates should be in ISO 8601 format: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS
# 4. Currency is in ZAR (South African Rand)
# 5. Authentication required for all endpoints except /health, /login, /register, /support/contact, /support/faq
# 6. Use Ctrl+Alt+R (Windows/Linux) or Cmd+Alt+R (Mac) to run requests
